{"tid":1115813,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多樂器老師會教 用耳仔彈翻隻歌","createTime":"2019-04-19T12:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T15:37:02.000Z","uid":245750,"like":127,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"96e26310e6a04baa14d78b1c79a37e9fc3352ce7","tid":1115813,"uid":245750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:42:13.000Z","msg":"小弟小學一人一樂器 <br />\n小提琴老師靜係教我睇譜撳掣<br />\n純粹建立眼同手既協調<br />\n完全冇培育到aural skills<br />\n上到中學到無特別興趣就冇繼續玩<br />\n大學玩choir先知玩音樂要聽scale degree/ do re mi<br />\n<br />\n先知原來唔洗perfect pitch都可以樂器上彈翻腦入邊既旋律出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家基本上咩歌都可以牧童笛吹翻出黎<br />\n唔洗譜玩音樂堅係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他學過樂器既大佬<br />\n請問係我小學老師廢 定係自己個腦唔識應變<br />\naural skill係要特登有人教 定係自己領悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4c92a4f2bf9ca9025cb88579430943bd00d0cd","tid":1115813,"uid":38033,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:46:14.000Z","msg":"岩，家陣so fa name 都係鳩講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6749c629eb0606d48472116262d17ff95c840520","tid":1115813,"uid":88263,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"憑記憶喺琴上面砌返首歌嘅單音要教嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5983b16129463002b6d67d5e2d2c92e5900cbf","tid":1115813,"uid":82829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6749c629eb0606d48472116262d17ff95c840520","tid":1115813,"uid":88263,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"憑記憶喺琴上面砌返首歌嘅單音要教嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" cla